<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM1.10.5">
<l>kaṇṭāyē neñcē karumaṅkaḷ vāykkiṉṟō</l>
<l>reṇṭāṉu miṉṟiyē vanti yalumā</l>
<l>ṟuṇṭā ṉaiyula kēḻumōr mūvaṭi</l>
<l>koṇṭā ṉaikaṇṭu koṇṭaṉai nīyumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You have seen, heart – [our] karmas have culminated –</l>
<l>the way [we] come [and] advance without even any calculation;</l>
<l>you too saw [and] took in the one who has swallowed the seven worlds,</l>
<l>him who took it in once three steps.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
